<template>
    <v-container>
        <v-card>
            <v-card-title>
                Card Title
            </v-card-title>
            <v-card-subtitle>
                Card Subtitle
            </v-card-subtitle>
            <v-card-text>
                This is some text inside the card. You can put more content here.
            </v-card-text>
            <v-card-actions>
                <v-btn @click="handleClick">Click Me</v-btn>
            </v-card-actions>
        </v-card>
    </v-container>
</template>

<script>
export default {
    name: 'NavbarComponent',
    methods: {
        handleClick() {
            alert('Button clicked!');
        }
    }
}
</script>

<style scoped>
/* Optional: Add your custom styles here */
</style>
